Package: stminsights
Type: Package
Title: A Shiny Application for Inspecting Structural Topic Models
Version: 0.1.2
Date: 2018-02-12
Authors@R: person("Carsten", "Schwemmer", email = "carsten.schwemmer@methodds.de",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/methodds/stminsights
Description: This app enables interactive validation, interpretation and visualization of structural topic models by Roberts and others (2014) <doi:10.1111/ajps.12103>. It also includes helper functions for model diagnostics and extracting data from effect estimates.
